title: Don Jose's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local restaurant chain offering mostly Mexican food. This outlet also makes pasta. The regular menu is meat-based but ask for the "healthy menu" which has choices of quinoa and brown rice for entrees. Could request to make the vegetarian items vegan.
